    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] was interviewed on November 7, 1957,",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "at which time he advised that his name is [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "that he is also known as [REDACTED] that he was born",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "on February 19, 1926, in Warsaw, Poland, and that he was",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "a German prisoner of war from May, 1942, until the Summer",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "of 1945. [REDACTED] advised that he arrived in New York on",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "May 2, 1951, as a displaced person, Alien Registration",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "Number [REDACTED] He advised that during 1944, while he was",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "a German prisoner of war, he observed a vehicle described",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "as circular in shape, seventy-five to one hundred yards in",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "diameter, and approximately fourteen feet high. He stated",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "the vehicle was observed to rise vertically to a height",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "sufficient to clear a fifty-foot wall and that it moved",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "slowly horizontally a short distance out of view which was",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "obstructed by trees. He stated that the engine of a",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "tractor failed to operate during this period and that the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "engine failed on one other occasion when a high-pitched",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "whining noise was heard in the area. During the interview,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "[REDACTED] spoke in a rational manner with no indication of",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "mental instability.",
